etes from having sex with each other.\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1569, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However,many individuals staying at the Olympic Village have posted videosshowing that the beds are perfectly durable.\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1734, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1804, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1821, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is concern about the comfort of the beds, though.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes will be desperate to experience good sleep in Paris to ensure they are in top condition for their events, with many expecting to travel home with medals.\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 2043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1936, \"end\": 1941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997262421, \"rank\": 2.7373153662306553e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A lack of sleep may prevent them from performing to the best of their abilities.\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2235, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2312, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2345, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Meanwhile, Saturday saw the start of all the main events at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2443, \"ent